    {
      "id": "26.11-6",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "Cw = (100∑i=1^n(hi/h)^2 * Ai) / (AB[1 + 0.83(hi/Di)^2])",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "left",
      "expression": "Cw = (100∑(hi/h)^2 * Ai) / (AB[1 + 0.83(hi/Di)^2])",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.11-7",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "where\nh = Mean roof height, ft (m);\nn = Number of shear walls in the building effective in resisting lateral forces in the direction under consideration;\nAB = Base area of the building, ft² (m²);\nAi = Horizontal cross-sectional area of shear wall i, ft² (m²);\nDi = Length of shear wall i, ft (m); and\nhi = Height of shear wall i, ft (m).",
