    {
      "id": "26.11-8",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "where Iz is the intensity of turbulence at height z̄, and z̄ is the equivalent height of the building or structure defined as 0.6h, but not less than zmin, for all building or structure heights h. zmin and c are listed for each exposure in Table 26.11-1; gQ and gv shall be taken as 3.4. The background response Q̄ is given by",
      "cross_references": [
        "Table 26.11-1"
      ],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.11-9",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "Q̄ = √(1/(1 + 0.63((B+h)/Lz)^0.63)) (26.11-8)",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "Q̄ = √(1/(1 + 0.63((B+h)/Lz)^0.63))",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.11-10",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "where B and h are defined in Section 26.3, and Lz is the integral length scale of turbulence at the equivalent height given by",
      "cross_references": [
        "26.3"
      ],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.11-11",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "Lz = ℓ(z̄/33)^ε̄ (26.11-9)",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "Lz = ℓ(z̄/33)^ε̄",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.11-12",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "Lz = ℓ(z̄/10)^ε̄ (26.11-9.SI)",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0,
        "x_end": 1,
        "y_start": 0,
        "y_end": 1
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "Lz = ℓ(z̄/10)^ε̄",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "26.11-13",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "in which ℓ and ε̄ are constants listed in Table 26.11-1.",
